<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Pudgalavada" title="Pudgalavada">Pudgalavada</a>
<ul><li>Vātsīputrīya</li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Saṃmitīya" title="Saṃmitīya" class="mw-redirect">Saṃmitīya</a></li></ul></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Sarvastivada" title="Sarvastivada">Sarvāstivāda</a>
<ul><li>(Haimavata)</li>
<li>(<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Kāśyapīya" title="Kāśyapīya">Kāśyapīya</a>)</li>
<li>(<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Mahīśāsaka" title="Mahīśāsaka">Mahīśāsaka</a>)
<ul><li>(<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Dharmaguptaka" title="Dharmaguptaka">Dharmaguptaka</a>)</li></ul></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Sautrāntika" title="Sautrāntika">Sautrāntika</a></li>
